==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Archeozoic
<hw>Archeozoic</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <fr>1</fr> <def>the time
from 1.5 billion to 5 billion years ago, when the earth's crust was
formed; the time when only unicellular organisms and the earliest forms
of life are present. Same as <er>Archaeozoic</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Archaeozoic, Archeozoic era, Archaeozoic
era</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

